citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:22 am on 18-DEC-
2023. The inspector spoke to a family member who stated the licensee was not available for an inspection today. A facility
representative was also called and they were unavailable for inspection today.
End Section
